snippet.title: Mega Man 11: Demo and Bounce Man Trailer
snippet.description: The Mega Man 11 demo is now live for PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch in North America and Europe! Grab the demo, check out Block Man’s stage, and share a screenshot of your victory with #BustBlockMan!
